  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      cross sectional study to detect frequency of functional gastrointestinal disorders among
      schhol aged children complaining of recurrent abdominal pain
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      school aged children from age of 5 to age of 15 who are complaining of recurrent abdominal
      pain will be included in the study , detailed history , examination and investigations will
      be done
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
